.DS_Store
.AppleDouble
.LSOverride
._*

# ── Xcode ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
## User-specific settings (window positions, breakpoints, schemes)
xcuserdata/
*.xcuserstate

## Build artifacts
DerivedData/
build/
*.moved-aside

## Index & workspace state
*.xcworkspace/xcshareddata/IDEWorkspaceChecks.plist

# ── Swift Package Manager ─────────────────────────────────────────
## SPM build output
.build/
Package.resolved

## Per-user SPM/Xcode data inside .swiftpm bundles
**/.swiftpm/xcode/xcuserdata/
**/.swiftpm/xcode/package.xcworkspace/xcuserdata/

# ── Swift Playgrounds ─────────────────────────────────────────────
## Playground execution logs (regenerated on run)
timeline.xctimeline
playground.xcworkspace

